data.value: WELCOME to TPF/DDS tools! This tool is designed to do anything and everything with DDS and TPF files (except edit DDS) in ALL three games. ----------------Overview------------------- You can load TPF's and most images incl DDS from the load menu, or drop and drag. You can then see details about the images including a preview. Analysing compares the images against the Texplorer tree to find a match. If found, details about the tree texture will also be displayed. You can save all loaded images into a .mod, install them to the game, and convert textures between formats. --------------------------------------------- Click Help for more information.
